[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜并没有急匆匆带我去见干娘。她告诉我，在正式拜访之前，她还需要做一些准备。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女如此郑重其事的模样，让我不免感受到些压力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而得知她接下来的目的地后，又让我有些困惑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "要买礼物的话，在公司旁边的商业街不就好了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哼哼，分析员这就不懂了吧，本天师今日观过天象，那条商业街被黑气笼罩，贸然前往，怕是有无妄之灾。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女一副言之凿凿，煞有介事的模样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说人话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我伸出一只手，以弹指的姿势接近卜卜的额头。她登时像是小兔子往后蹦了两步，双马尾飞扬着，然后弱弱捂住额头，嚣张的气势一下子弱了下去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可恶，分析员就只会这样欺负我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她鼓了鼓脸颊扭过头，用心虚且害臊的语气开口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我过去在那条街发过传单，被人赶走了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你还做过这种兼职？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过只是发传单的话，为什么要赶走你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个……说来话长。反正本天师是不会去那种险要之地的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再说了，那里卖的东西都死贵死贵的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没关系，你的分析员颇有家资。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "第一次拜访干娘的礼物，怎么也不该让卜卜来操心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不行，不能让分析员花冤枉钱。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就算分析员不心疼，我也会心疼。我才不要这样浪费分析员的钱。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜微微撅嘴表达不满。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是是是！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "最终，我还是被卜卜带到了市郊的一条商业街。商业街入口最显眼的，是一只模样奇怪的大猫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么样，很棒吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜蹦到大猫的身边，拍了拍它敦实的身体，她的表情很是得意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "确实很棒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我指的是人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是吧！这可是本天师的杰作！",
        "disable": 0
